-----------------------------
vtiger CRM 4.2 Documentation
-----------------------------
Please refer to the following URLs for installation procedure in various operations systems.

(A) vtiger CRM 4.2: 

	1. Windows: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_CRM_Installation_Guide_Windows.pdf

	2. Linux: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_CRM_Installation_Guide_Linux.pdf

	3. LAMP/WAMP: Please refer to the "Installing  Only vtiger CRM" section in vtiger CRM 4 Windows and Linux Installation Guides.

	4. User Manual: http://www.vtiger.com/wiki/index.php/Vtiger_CRM_-_User_Guide (vtiger Community based documentation) 

(B) vtiger CRM 4.2 Add-ons:
 
	1. vtiger Outlook Plug-in 4.2: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_Outlook_Plugin_User_Guide.pdf

	2. vitger Office Plug-in 4.2: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_Office_Plugin_User_Guide.pdf

	3. vtiger Thunderbird Extension 4.2: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_Thunderbird_Extension_User_Guide.pdf
 
	4. vtiger Customer Portal 4.2: http://vtiger.com/products/crm/help/vtiger_Customer_Portal_User_Guide.pdf
